{"title":"党召唤我们的时候……","authors":["科尔内留·谢尔班"],"dates":[{"year":1978,"month":8,"day":18}],"parts":[{"type":"paragraph","text":"党召唤我们的时候……"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"〔罗马尼亚〕科尔内留·谢尔班"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"一个更加美好、更加正义的世"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"界，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"我们已经开始全力去缔造；"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"我们心里孕育着一支热情的颂"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"歌，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"歌唱人民的雄心壮志和庄严情"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"操。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"我是共产党人，这高尚的称"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"号，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"首先意味着重任在肩："},{"type":"paragraph","text":"要以永不停息的战斗作行动，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"对人民的热爱和忠诚坚定不"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"变！"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"当人民不断贡献劳动果实"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"时，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"我们永远做得很不够，不管对"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"国家的贡献有多少；"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"在党召唤着我们的时候，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"我们一生都要时刻响应她发出"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"的号召。"}],"comments":[],"comment_pivots":[],"description":"","page_start":3,"page_end":3}